# Root .env.example — reference only.
# Actual env files live in client/.env and server/.env (each has its own .env.example).
# This file documents which variables exist where so you don't have to hunt.
#
# client/.env      -> VITE_API_URL, VITE_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY
# server/.env      -> DATABASE_URL, JWT_SECRET, REFRESH_TOKEN_SECRET, STRIPE_SECRET_KEY,
#                     RESEND_API_KEY, CLIENT_URL, NODE_ENV, PORT
